title: DAC7578 Breakout Back Side with Size Reference
summary: Back-side product photo of the DAC7578 board next to a US quarter for scale. Rear silkscreen text includes default and broadcast I2C addresses and operating voltage.

structured_data.description: Rear of board shows pin holes and silkscreen labels including 'DAC7578', 'I2C Octal 12bit DAC', 'Default I2C Addr 0x4C', 'Broadcast Address 0x47', and 'VLogic/Vcc: 3-5VDC'. A US quarter coin is placed to the right for size comparison.
